{"tid":1714200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔經四條柱/崇基入中大","createTime":"2019-11-13T00:11:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T00:34:30.000Z","uid":233173,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1a8b19a82a2fd9f4f7af351e85650d0892d6ae27","tid":1714200,"uid":233173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:11:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p9WQ1nY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp9WQ1nY.jpg&h=97170ae0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天賦海灣有條橋向大埔舊路 跨過左吐露港公路之後會見到左手邊有個細路口 行過去就係敬文書院附近<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔該全世界入嚟救中大</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f607aeb4c617c2ec818828f9bb9429dff86c7d9e","tid":1714200,"uid":233173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:11:38.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"44d7727517db266798d0e76ade4e6af5c38353a8","tid":1714200,"uid":233173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:11:54.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"a7bf29db7e95c5d1480e63efe22129ade9798462","tid":1714200,"uid":278228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:12:05.000Z","msg":"借po一個位<br />\n大家好，示威其實都4個月<br />\n我地每次行動都會影響到民生，<br />\n琴日我係沙田去暴大，<br />\n沿途好多街彷屌road block，又話過分乜乜77<br />\n但冇人提過黑警好似殺人咁攻中大<br />\n因為呢件事<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔關佢事</span></strong></span><br />\n每次咁辛苦做咁多野，到頭嚟都係要比人屌<br />\n既然係咁，<br />\n大家係咪時候諗下要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">直搗皇龍</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔關政見問題，係有的確為所不少既人只關注生計<br />\n同有冇屋企番，甚至會主動清road block<br />\n即使唔係撐警<br />\n既然守中大又要送頭，守旺角又要通頂<br />\n但係都迫唔到政府做啲乜<br />\n<br />\n4個月喇<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>點解宜家仲唔升級去搞啲官</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n至少仲會多人支持<br />\n<br />\n策略：小隊突擊，人在明我在暗"},{"pid":"4d7d34d922f28544cac4a2543a84be393d1f2b52","tid":1714200,"uid":233173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:12:16.000Z","msg":"五大訴求"},{"pid":"98e9e36c0457d7f719b11ba640e326b5368e250e","tid":1714200,"uid":233173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:12:36.000Z","msg":"缺一不可"},{"pid":"10306a5027cb6abad9929595ffcb349cef7d84ba","tid":1714200,"uid":233173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:13:02.000Z","msg":"天滅共產黨"},{"pid":"5777af72d36400addf0ea1e7a0bdb2346c69350e","tid":1714200,"uid":233173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:13:21.000Z","msg":"全黨死清光"},{"pid":"ba2c3f897f0917a740f82bcdb916fa25707b4230","tid":1714200,"uid":79599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:13:55.000Z","msg":"襯返工時間<br />\n當自己係中大返工<br />\n無人可以阻止"},{"pid":"3759f90b93be80185c616e04a63831a3746d4bf8","tid":1714200,"uid":69741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:14:07.000Z","msg":"即係你咁揚係咪想狗block埋佢呢"},{"pid":"019a88aa25df0d68ff4ff380f98873a9868b4d19","tid":1714200,"uid":146454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:14:40.000Z","msg":"敬文附近<br />\n你確定真係入到中大？<br />\n利申暴大撚"},{"pid":"2c8188af5c58c1106d9dc492fb62096ad1ba76c4","tid":1714200,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:14:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b48e80f68256d2c7a42ce8de0c6d45ec36684f","tid":1714200,"uid":233173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:14:43.000Z","msg":"香港人 反抗"},{"pid":"8ce8d5b6ee93ff7754dbb13a22ff89c55ff09abd","tid":1714200,"uid":31752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3759f90